We bring in scholars in the
humanities and social sciences

00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:08.230
by appointment of the Librarian
or by competitive processes.

00:03:08.230 --> 00:03:09.990
To take advantage of
the library collections.

00:03:09.990 --> 00:03:12.100
And we're really
pleased that this event,

00:03:12.100 --> 00:03:16.100
featuring Davide Ceriani,
who is a Kluge Fellow,

00:03:16.100 --> 00:03:19.900
is a part of the
European Month of Culture.

00:03:19.900 --> 00:03:23.860
First let me recognize
Emanuele Amendola.

